  M7-ku2 i-e5 phin2-seng3-tiong te7 it tu3-hian7 e5 si7 siok8 ti7 u2-tiu7-lai7 kek8 khui-khoah. Lan2 thau5-chit8-e7 thak8 Ki-tok-toan7 thang ki5-iN7 e5, si7 Ki-tok e5 it-gian5 it-heng7, bo5 hou7 si5-tai7 jin5-cheng2 sou2 han7-tiaN7. Tng-si5 khoaN3 Ki-tok cho3 Iu5-thai3 lang5, ia7 bo5 chhiuN7 Iu5-thai3 lang5 ; Iu5-thai3-lang5 jiat8-sim hi-le2 toa7 khoaN3-khin goa7-pang, m7-ku2 Ki-tok bo5 chhiuN7 in kok-bin5 e5 seng3. Chiu7 kong2 i si7 Lo5-ma2 lang5, m7-ku2 Ki-tok bo5 Lo5-ma2-lang5 chhut-sek e5 lut8-hoat cheng3-ti7, bu2-lat8 e5 phai3-thau5. KhoaN3 Ki-tok cho3 Hi-liap8 lang5, ia7 bo5 chhin-chhiuN7 Hi-liap8 lang5 houN3 ti3-sek heng3 su-siuN2 hit khoan2. 
