  Tang sai e5 hian5-jin5 tiat8-su7 sou2 thang kho2-chhu2--e5, chiu7-si7 kou2-bu2 iong2-beng2 e5 sim chin7-lat8 lai5 siam2-pi7 choe7-ok. Chong2--si7 Ki-tok to7-tek e5 phin2-seng3 si7 oan5-choan5 bo5 ha5-hun5, m7-bat u7 hoan7-choe7, ia7 m7-bat jin7 u7 choe7-ok ; chiu7 sui-si7 tioh8 hoe2-gou7 tioh8 sia3-choe7, hit ho7 e5 siuN7-liam7 ia7 bo5 ; hoan2-tng2 ho2-taN2 kong-gian5 u7 sia3 lang5 choe7 e5 koan5. Chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2 e5 phin2-seng3 ti7 jin5-kan e5 lek8-su2 boe7-bat u7 khoaN3-kiN3 ; iu7-koh ia7 bo5 lang5 phu5-phio3 e5 sim. 
  Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 beh kong2, Ki-tok sui-jian5 chai-kio3 u7 choe7, iau2-ku2 ui7-tioh8 pat8-hang7 bok8-tek phian3 ka-ti7, khoa-khau2 kong2 na7-tiaN7. Chong2--si7 bo5 lun7 tui3 to2-ui7 khoaN3 si7 ho2 lang5 bo5 chho3 e5 Ki-tok, kan-ta chit-hang7-su7 lai5 ke2-cho3, tau3-ti2 be7 thang sin3. Ki-tok e5 phin2-seng3 bo5 thang pi2 e5 su7, sui-jian5 iau2 u7 pat8 mih8 thang kong2, chong2--si7 i siok8 ti7 u2-tiu7 lai7 kek8 khoah-toa7, kap oan5-choan5, thang siuN7 si7 nng7 hang7 e5 toa7 chhut-sek. Ki-tok-kau3 e5 ui2-tai7 si7 tui3 Ki-tok phin2-seng3 e5 koan5, toa7. 
  Te7 Ji7. Ki-tok-kau3 ui2-tai7 e5 iau3-tiam2 si7 i pi7-pan7 e5 ku2-tng5. Ki-tok-kau3 iu5-lai5 e5 ku2 pat8 e5 chong-kau3 be7 thang kap i pi2-tit. Hoe5-hoe5-kau3 long2 bo5 sim2-mih8 chun2-pi7, kan-ta chiau3 Mou5-han2-bek8-tek e5 kiam3-kng chhut-hian7 ti7 se3-kan. Iu5-thai3 kau3 cho3 I2-sek-liat8 bin5-chok8 e5 chong-kau3, put-ko3 si7 chhut Ai-kip8 liau2-au7 50 jit8 ku2 na7-tiaN7. Ki5-thaN chiah-e5 kau3 e5 heng khi2 ia7 bo5 leng7-goa7 ku2-tng5 i7-pi7 siat-hoat. Ki-tok-kau3 lai5 chit se3-kan ti7 lang5 e5 lek8-su2 tiong m7-si7 choan5-jian5 kou-lip8 e5 su7, si7 ku2-ku2 u7-pi7 chit8 si5-tai7 koe3 chit8 si5-tai7, bo5 choat8-tng7 lai5 hoat-tat8 e5 kau3. Hit lai7-tiong u7 loa7-che7 te3 ong5 heng-khi2, sian-ti gau5 lang5 chhut-hian7 ka7 Ki-tok chun2-pi7. Koh khah thang chai--e5 chiu7-si7 Iu5-thai3 lang5 u7 teh theng3-hau7 chu7 cha2-cha2 Siong7-te3 sou2 iok Bi2-sai3-a kang3-lim5 ; ia7 pat8 kok lang5 u7 teh ng3-bang7 Sin5 hoa3-sin beh kap lang5 chhin-kin7 e5 su7. Pou3-le2-to7 ( Plato ) u7 sin3 be7 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 Kiu3-chu2 beh lai3 ; Lo5-ma2 e5 lek8-su2-ka Ta-si-ta-su ( Tacitus ) ti7 i e5 chheh-tiong ia7 tai7-seng kong2, Se3-kai3 e5 Kiu3-chu2 beh lai5. An2-ni Ki-tok si7 cho3 Hi-pek-lai5 sian-ti sou2 kong2 e5 Bi2-sai3-a, ban7-kok ban7-bin5 sou2 ng3-bang7 ; li7 taN nng7-chheng-ni5 cheng5 chiau3 hit-si5 e5 te7-li2 sou2 kong2 si7 se3-kai3 tiong-sim e5 Iu5-thai3-kok hia chhut-si3. I e5 iu5-lai5 e5 ku2 chin-chiaN3 thang kong2, Hi-pek-lai5 lang5 e5 sin3-kho3, Hi-liap8-lang5 e5 kok-gu2, Lo5-ma2-lang5 e5 lut8-hoat sit8-chai7 si7 cho3 I e5 in2-lou7--lah !
  Te7 saN hang7. Ki-tok-kau3 ui2-tai7 e5 iau3-kiaN7 si7 u7 kek8 toa7 e5 kam2-hoa3 hou7 se3-kan. Ki-tok pi2-pheng7 thian-kok cho3 koa3-chhai3-chi2, sui-jian5 pi2 pah hang7 e5 cheng2-chi2 khah se3, kau3 toa7-chang5 khah toa7 pat8 hang7 e5 chhai3-se, giam2-jian5 chiaN5 chhiu7, poe-chiau2 lai5 hioh ti7 i e5 ki. Chit e5 phi3-ju7 si7 teh kong2 Ki-tok-kau3 goa7-bin7 e5 chin3-pou7. Koh kong2, thian-kok chhin-chhiuN7 kaN3-bu2, hu7-jin5-lang5 theh8 khi3 khng3 ti7 saN tau2 mi7-hun2 lai7, kau3 long2-chong2 hoat-kaN3. Che2 si7 teh kong2 Ki-tok-kau3 sim-leng5-lai7 e5 kiat koe2-chi2. Goa2 siuN7 ai3 tui3 chit nng7 peng5 lai5 lun7 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 kam2-hoa3. 
  Ki-tok e5 su7-giap8 kan-ta 2, 3 ni5 kan ti7 Iu5-thai3 kok thoan5-to7, poaN3-chiuN7-lou7-e7 ti7 sip8-ji7-ke3 teng2 siu7 chhi-chham2, kam2-si7 seng5-kong e5 su7-giap8 mah ? I lai5 ka-ti7 e5 kok, ka-ti7 e5 peh-seN3 m7 chiap-lap8 i. Ki-tok ti7 te7-bin7-chiuN7 e5 su7-giap8 thang kong2 si7 choan5-jian5 sit-pai7. Koh tng-si5 e5 hak8-seng ko2-jian5 u7 e7-kham-tit cho3 chiaN5 Ki-tok sou2 lau5 e5 giap8 e5 jin5-but8 a2-bo5 ? Khiok in si7 seng5-sit8 tiong-tit8 e5 chhau2-te7 lang5, na7 lun7 se3-su7 sia7-hoe7 e5 te7-ui7 a2-si7 hak8-bun7 e5 koan5-leng5 khui3-lat8 si7 long2 bo5 poaN3-hang7. M7-ku2 tui3 Kau3-chou2 si2-au7 boe7 chit8 pah ni5-kan, chhin-chhiuN7 koa3-chhai3-chi2 hiah toa7 e5 thian-kok, khui-khoah ti7 Te7-tiong-hai2 ian5-hoaN7. KhoaN3 che2 chin-chiaN3 thang kong2 Ki-tok kau3-hoe7 e5 siat-lip8, ti7 su2-ki3 tiong u7 bo5 thang pi2 e5 sit8-cheng5. Chu2-au7 300 ni5 tng-si5 chong2-lang2 se3-kai3 e5 koan5 Lo5-ma2 e5 Hong5-te3 Khong2-su7-tan3-teng cho3 Ki-tok-kau3-tou5. U7 lang5 teh gi5 Hong5-te3 hoan2-hoe2 e5 sim; siat-su2 Hong5-te3 hoan2-hoe2 e5 sim na7 bo5 chin-sit8, chiu7 tek-khak hou7 thong-kok e5 lang5 gi2-gi7 ap-che3. Tui3 an2-ni lai5 khoaN3 hit-si5 Ki-tok-kau3 ti7 Lo5-ma2 sou2 tit-tioh8 e5 se3-lek8 si7 choaN2-iuN7 thang chai--lah ? Cheng5 hou7 lang5 sou2 kheng-bu2 e5 sip8-ji7-ke3 taN cho3 kok-ki5 e5 ki3-ho7, cho3 te3 ong5 heng-cheng5 chun-kui3 e5 kong-pai5. Koh Ki-tok kang3-seng e5 ni5-ko7, siong7 tui3 cheng3-hu2 ha7 kau3 ban7-bin5 long2 teh eng7. 
  Ki-tok-kau3 ti7 se3-kai3 chhong3-siat ban7-kok kok-che3 e5 sin hong-siok8. Pun2-te2 kok-kok e5 lang5 khoaN3 goa7-kok lang5 cho3 tui3-tek8, taN tui3 Ki-tok-kau3 hou7 te7-kiu5 teng2 e5 kok-bin5 saN chhin-kin7 ho5-hok8. Khi2-thau5 tu3 Kok-che3 lun5-li2 e5, si7 Iu2-go Gu-lo-sia-su ( Hugo Grotius ); u7 lang5 pheng5 i sou2 tu3 e5 chheh kong2,“ I sou2 tu3 chhut-mia5 e5 kok-che3-hoat si7 eng7 Sin-Ku7-iok cho3 te7-ki. I tu3-sut8 e5 su-siuN2 si7 chhut tui3 Ki-tok-kau3 phok-ai3 sun5-choan5 e5 cheng-sin5. ” Sou2 phoe-pheng5 chin tioh8. Hian7-kim e5 Kok-che3-lun5-li2 sui boe7 thang sng3 cho3 chiau5-chng5 ho2, chong2--si7 tui3 che2 u7 kou2-bu2 se3-kai3 jin5-to7-chu2-gi7, hit-e5 kong-lo5 sit8-chai7 toa7. Ki-tok-kau3 ui7-tioh8 jin5-to7 chin7-lat8 hian3-sin e5 su7, chit8 hang7 chit8-hang7 kong2 be7 chin7. Lo5-lin3-gu5 Bu2-le5-su ( Loring Brace ) e5 Jin5-to7 hoat-tat8 su2 sou2 ku2-khi2-e5 thang kong2 u7 tit-tioh8 i e5 iau3-leng2, taN sia2 lai5 tui3 khoaN3 chiu7-si7 :--
  Keng3-tiong7 loan2-jiok8 kap san3-hiong e5 jin5-keh; chun-keng3 hu7-jin5; ho2-giah8 lang5 tui3 kan-khou2-lang5 e5 gi7-bu7; tui3-tiong7 siau2-ji5; po2-tiong7 kaN-hoan7, chhut-goa7 lang5, san3-hiong lang5, lian5 tong7-but8 ia7 tioh8. Koat-toan3 m7-thang iong5-un2 chan5-jim2 ap-che3 kap lou5-chai5 e5 chu2-gi7; toaN-sin lang5 chheng-khi3-siuN3 e5 gi7-bu7 ; kap kiat-hun e5 sin5-seng3 ; chun2-chat e5 iau3-kin2 ; cho3 kang than3 chiN5 kong-piN5 e5 hoat-tou7; chu-pun2 hap8-tang5; hoat-tat8 kok lang5 e5 chai5-leng5 kau3 kek8 ho2 e5 koan5-li7; tak8-lang5 thang hiong2-siu7 cheng3-ti7 sia7-hoe7 e5 koan5 ; chit8 kok-bin5 e5 ham7-hai7 si7 tak8 kok-bin5 e5 ham7-hai7 e5 goan5-li2 ; chu7-iu5 thong-siong kap kok-kok kau-che3 chu7-iu5 e5 su7. Boh8-tit chian3-cheng; na7 put-i2 tioh8 kau-chian3, tioh8 siat-hoat hou7 i chio2 ham7-hai7 ; koh u7 kok-che3 chhai5-phoaN3 lai5 ti5-hong5 kau-chian3 boe7 hoat-choh e5 tai7-seng. 
  I2-siong7 si7 Ki-tok-kau3 chu2-gi7, hian7-kim sit8-heng5 ti7 se3-kai3. KhoaN3 choe3-kin7 100 ni5 kan Ki-tok-kau3 e5 oah8-tang7 koh khah thang kiaN--tioh8:--chhin-chhiuN7 siat Chu2-jit8 oh8 ; Goa7-kok Soan-kau3 e5 su7-giap8 ; Chheng-lian5 hoe7 ; Kiu3-se3-kun ; Kiong7-le7 hoe7 ; Kim3-chiu2 hoe7 ; kai2-liong5 kaN gak8 ; po2-hou7 chhut-kaN lang5 ; kiu3-che3 pin5-bin5 ; ki5-u5 ng3-bang7 kai2-liong5 sia7-hoe7 e5 chong-kau3 un7-tong7 ; ke3-bou5 cho3 se3-kai3 e5 hok-khi3 hiah-e5 su7 chiau3 hian7-kim e5 sit8-cheng5 si7 lang5 lang5 sou2 chai. Chu2 e5 ki5-to2-bun5 kong2, “ Li2 e5 kok lim5-kau3 ”, taN khak-sit8 u7 teh eng3-giam7. 
  Chong2--si7 beh chong2-kiat lai5 lun7, tioh8 chiong long2-chong2 su7-cheng5 lai5 chham-kho2, na7 ai3 beng5 Ki-tok-kau3 Ui2-tai7 e5 seng3-chit : kan-ta chiong Ki-tok e5 phin2-seng3, I-e5 su7-giap8 kap su7-giap8 e5 goa7-pou7 sou2 hian2-beng5-e5, beh lai5 chiau5-chai si7 bo5 kau3-giap8 ; tek-khak tioh8 pah-chhioh e5 tek-ko thau5 koh chin3 chit pou7, pun2-sin chit8 lang5 chit8 lang5 siu7 tioh8 Ki-tok e5 kam2-hoa3 cho3 oah8-mia7, lai5 kang2-kiu3 chhiau-chhoe7 i lai7-bin7 e5 su7-sit8, chiah e7-eng7-tit. Ki-tok e5 su3-tou5 Po2-lo5 kong2, “ Goan2 bat goan2 e5 Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok.” I si7 tui3 sit8-giam7, sin5-leng5, pun2-sin lang5, lai5 bat Kiu3-chu2. Chit ho7 sit8-giam7 e5 ti3-sek si7 cho3 i lai7-tiong kek8-toa7 e5 lat8, cho3 i chit8-si3 lang5 e5 Chu2. “ Goa2 oah8, si7 ui7-tioh8 Ki tok ; si2, ia7 si7 goa2 e5 li7-ek “; an2-ni hou7 i hiah kam2-kek, pang3-sak chou2-sian ui-giam5 e5 chong-kau3, chun-kui3, te7-ui7, mia5-siaN, khoaN3 cho3 pun3-so3, ka-ti7 lai5 cho3 Ki-tok e5 lou5-pok8, thoan5 lang5 sou2 hiam5 e5 kau3 ia7 bo5 kian3-siau3. 
  Ki-tok-kau3 m7-si7 si2-sin3 e5 tiau5-kui, ia7-si7 chheng-khi3 e5 li2-siong2 (siuN7 hiah ho2 chiu7 hiah ho2), to7-tek ka3-si7 e5 oe7, ia7 m7-si7 thoan5-the2. Ki-tok-kau3 si7 hou7 lang5 oah8, hou7 lang5 teng5-thau5-siN, sin5 chin2-kiu3 e5 koan5-leng5 khui3-lat8. Ki-tok-kau3 m7-si7 oa2-kho3 chai5-leng5 bu2-lek8 ia7-si7 goa7-kau e5 chhiu2-toaN7, bok8-su e5 lat8 lai5 iaN5 se3-kan; si7 tui3 “tai7-seng chin2-kiu3 Iu5-thai3-lang5 kap chiah-e5 Hi-li7-ni5 lang5 kap hoan7-na7 sin3 e5 lang5 sin5 e5 lat8 e5 Hok-im”; khi2 Siong7-te3 e5 kok ti7 sim-leng5-teng2. Ki-tok-kau3 se3-lek8 e5 chhim koh toa7 si7 tui3 toaN-sin lang5 sit8-giam7 lai5 chai. Ki-tok-kau3 na7 ko2-jian5 u7 chiau3 goa2 teng2-bin7 sou2 kong2 i e5 kau3-chou2 e5 jin5-phin2, i e5 liau7-li2 chun2-pi7, kap sit8-chai7 e5 kam2-hoa3, pun2-sin lang5 sou2 bat chin2-kiu3 e5 sit8-giam7, ui2-tai7 e5 Seng3 chit-chai5 e5, an2-ni thang beng5-chai m7-si7 peng5-siong5 phou2-thong e5 chong-kau3 lah. Seng3-keng kong2: “Chhin-chhiuN7 hiah toa7 e5 chin2-kiu3 lan2 chiah-e5 khoaN3-choe3 bo5 iau3-kin2, chaiN2-iuN7 oe7 to5-siam2-tit” (Hi-pek-lai5 2:3)? Ban7-it Ki-tok-kau3 e5 iau3-kiaN7 na7 khoaN3 loh8-kau khi3, ia7-si7 m7 jin7 soa3 li7-khui, che si7 hou7 tui3-tiong7 sit8-bu7 bo5 kap che kin7-se3-tai7 e5 cheng-sin5 saN-siang7, chiau3-li2-khi3 lai5 kang2-kiu3 hit-ho7 chi3-khi3 e5 lang5 sou2 bo5 chhu2.
